Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huntsman of Belparaso, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:08.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Samagui!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:13.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go shoot down Layla's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:48.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Samagui of Belparaso!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:50.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I know him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:55.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's used as the basis for \Nchildren's books up north.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A living legendary huntsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Human Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:07.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind: Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:09.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Angle: Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would a huntsman shoot a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even from that posture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast, human, it matters not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it my master's order, I will hunt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:29.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing high in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That angle's nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the reason I made \Nhim meh subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:44.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His shooting ability is far beyond that \Nof some wizard shooting a magic gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not if I can help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:52.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He did that to my arrows with rubble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:57.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skills are indeed impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But not up to the level of Sagittarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up after that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A huntsman never lets his prey escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:09.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... "That woman"? "Prey"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's beyond insulting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:37.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,According to what Crux said, you were \Ncontracted with Layla 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:43.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And although I'm not sure what \Ndeal happened in the human world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:49.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,your master now is Layla's daughter, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like Lucy \Nknows this herself, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:58.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what exactly happened, Capricorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:07.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each and every magic has some \Nrule which cannot be violated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As for meh, I tried to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the result is this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:19.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A goat! Go ahead and laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:28.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Around that time, Natsu and Happy, \Nhaving sensed the enemy's presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:34.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,or rather, smelled their scent, were \Nheading deeper into Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His smell is this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:38.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The path isn't very good, so \Nyou should watch your step!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He got quiet all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets nauseous sliding on leaves? Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:10.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't hurt... at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:15.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:18.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a small sapling there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:39.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Time Ark has guided the \Nsapling to its future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:44.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where your future \Nleads, Natsu Dragneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one from back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:50.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely the same smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who used Lyon and \Nthe others in Galuna Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is dressin' in women's clothing \Nyour hobby or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:02.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That would explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is what I really look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:09.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the 7 Kin of \NPurgatory of Grimoire Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear Milkovich.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul-Tea Milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trip over your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:20.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're after Zeref, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is... Zeref?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:33.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy made Lullaby and Deliora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref is a person from a long, long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have him, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd want 'im?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:49.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna forgive you guys when you \Ndon't even care about your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I suppose I'd better pay \Nyou back for that last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:57.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this time, for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:03.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, Erza and Juvia \Nhad gone to gather their comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:07.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,immediately after hearing of the \Nattack, and before them appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia Lockser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A former member of Phantom \NLord's Elemental Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus Titania, Erza Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you have already researched \Nabout Juvia and Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,State your name, villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not deem answering that as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:28.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:32.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Juvia is worried about Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to be by his side soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:39.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! What if Gray-sama is \Nin big trouble right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:48.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... is it so hard to breathe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart, it aches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:53.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has taken a hold of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:58.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I was too weak to \Nbe your partner after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to be such a spoiler!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought your best partner with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You came for me, Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:12.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The shortness of breath, the \Nthing that's grabbed my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was you, Juvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:20.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us are S Class partners \Nrecognized throughout the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, throughout the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you try {\i1}concentrating{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:37.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maguilty Sodom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's coming for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic blades?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She can summon weapons as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia's body is made of water!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the attack, Juvia will not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:03.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia's body made of water... was injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My blades attack the sense of pain directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they are "sensory blades".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:10.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be one of the 7 Kin of Purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not deem answering that as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:21.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe out the enemy. That is my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:27.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've started to get a bit nostalgic \Nfor the body of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:36.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Human Subordination Magic, Humaraise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am a Spirit, not a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:46.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... And that is why this is taboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic cannot be used \Non those who are not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm suddenly in a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who breaks this rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are fused together...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:12.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're actually Capricorn \Nthat's been fused with a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:19.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll take your body, Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to stand around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:51.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think maybe it'd be better to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel, but we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke had a reason for what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:02.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd get in his way if we were around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you shouldn't be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the leader of the 12 \NZodiac Gates, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's get together with the \Nothers and go search for the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:18.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke... You'd better come back safe to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Meh attack from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:50.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've finally gotten \Nmy hands on a human form!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:01.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been good to me until now, goat body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't move after taking Leo's attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:09.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meh name... I mean, my name is Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My master is Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy Heartfilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:19.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can kill that master, then \NI can become a perfect human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:25.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. Lucy trusts this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I shall catch her off guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe I'll subjugate her and \Nplay around for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful, like Layla-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Regulus is full.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:47.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Zoldio-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:52.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare say that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Capricorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do apologize for having to be a bit rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:06.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You had to be, or separating \Nhim would have been impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:13.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can you move, Capricorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:17.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately when you fused with Leo-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:22.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he gave me the light of the king, Regulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That... was giving you magic power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm finally back to my original body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:43.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:46.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:52.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Capricorn, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me... Layla-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:02.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such is the fate of those \Nwho break the taboos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla-sama retired from Wizardry \Nto preserve her health.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:26.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She bequeathed Cancer-sama, Aquarius-sama, \Nand meh to three of her servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:32.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them was Zoldio-sama, \Nand he received meh key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:38.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Layla and meh made one final contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:44.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I pledge to protect your \Nfamily for now to eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:50.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If in the future, your offspring \Nchooses to walk the path of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:57.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that time comes, please \Nhelp them, Capricorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:02.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how Lucy became your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoldio-sama consented to \Nthat contract at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:12.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but soon after he left the mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and while wandering aimlessly, he ended \Nup being touched by dark magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:23.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He violated the taboo, and fused with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes strong magic power will \Nlead people to the dark side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:33.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is harder to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:41.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you think of Lucy-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is, indeed, Layla-sama's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:48.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know well how beloved she is by her \NSpirits, and how much she loves them in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll help, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll help Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:16:00.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-sama cannot borrow \Nmeh help at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:07.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For meh power has always been \NLucy-sama's from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally return to meh master's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:17.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen with Loke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he won!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can count on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'll explain more later, \Nbut Capricorn is on our side now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he needs to regain his energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:36.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so he's returning to the Spirit \NWorld as my Spirit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:42.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he was using his own magic power to \Nstay in the Human World until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about being my partner, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said to tell you he's sorry, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:54.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't given up on being S Class yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S Class...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up a second, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:08.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we split up to search \Nfor the 7 Kin of Purgatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't wanna go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Cana...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:22.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean split into two \Ngroups, not "split up".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wanna mix it up with the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:32.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be smarter to \Nattack with everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:36.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to attack the enemy \Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:39.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That way we can resume the S Class exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we should split up and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:45.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you scared to go alone, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll split up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:56.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, you nut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:09.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't gotten in my way, I'd \Nhave been an S Class wizard by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:29.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The other future of the \Nfractured crystal ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Parallel worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:36.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can create an infinite number of futures,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and contract them to head \Ntoward a single future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flash Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, the fun's just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the remains of the base camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them are breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:03.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:08.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But for Gajeel to get taken out in \Nthe process, and Mira to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:11.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not anyone's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:19.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:21.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:25.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it, but \Nthey're too damn strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure of a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:35.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to protect \Nmy sister or my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:50.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The exam had us all split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:56.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just for a bit, but we were \Nputting ourselves before our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, we can't do that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is extremely powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:05.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we are Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:10.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we all combine our power... \NIf we can act as one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's no way we'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Join together as one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:23.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mavis's grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:24.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me you'd figured \Nout where it was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:30.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened and it kind of took \Na backseat, but I'm curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:35.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's about halfway guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:40.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I thought of a lot of different \Nwords associated with "grave".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:47.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Death, sleep, earth, stone, star, end...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of them were 6 letters long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:53.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... What does being 6 letters \Nhave to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:59.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said we had to find it in 6 hours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:01.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit ham-fisted,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I found a word that's 6 letters for \N6 hours and associated with a grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:10.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It means to perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's related to a grave and also 6 letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It includes the concept of time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:23.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the rest is just intuition, but demise \Nhas a letter that doesn't fit with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:25.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:28.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one letter that was used twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,E. Doesn't that strike you as odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:39.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, the paths we chose \Nwere lettered, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the ones from the first test?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:43.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Route E!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:47.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's in... there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:58.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some kind of special move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.51,0:24:00.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Roar, or Iron Fist, or Claws...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:02.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:04.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:05.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:08.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there is a special move!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.31,0:24:09.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:12.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Lucy on fire, and \Nchuck her at the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.66,0:24:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I call it:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:14.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then that's basically \Na special move for Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.56,0:24:22.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but if Lucy's the bullet \Nthat's basically mine, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, do you even understand the point?
